data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT * Located on a bustling street, it offers a unique blend of character and convenience.  The extraordinary architecture and mature landscaping provide a sense of character, while the interior boasts ample space for a family or those who love room to spread out.  The property's busy street location means easy access to amenities yet still a neighborhood atmosphere.  It's a perfect choice for those who appreciate the charm of older homes and the excitement of a lively urban setting. *  Carpet in Basement bedroom has been replaced *
